h&s new faculty furniture allocation page 1 h&s new faculty furniture allocation purpose to help departments with the cost of setting up new faculty offices eligibility all newly hired regular tenure track faculty members are eligible senior lecturers emeriti fixed term appointments and other visitors are not eligible parameters $900 will be transferred into each department's budget savings for each new faculty member unused money will carry forward procedures the h&s finance office will transfer the funding into the department's budget savings when a list of faculty who have accepted appointments is received these entries will be made as ijournal fund transfers and will not be added to the commitments database please submit requests to your finance liaison
